   <head>To children and seruants.</head>
   <p>Sanctifie the Lord God in your hearts, and bee readie alwayes to giue an answer to every man that asketh you a reason of the hope that is in you, with meekne<gap reason="illegible" resp="#keyers" extent="2 letters">
         <desc>••</desc>
      </gap>e and feare. 1 <hi>peter.</hi> 3. 15.</p>
